name: Guru Made Homestay
address: Jl. Bongan Lebah Kelod, Bongan, Kec. Tabanan, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: The rooms are simple but comfortable. No Ac but simple fan is very helpful. The owner is super friendly and very informative without being chatty. The breakfast is great. I had fried rice with special balinese black coffee and some fruits. So grateful to find this place for my temporary stay in Kediri. If anything can be improved is the bathroom quality, the water and the insects (ants). Other than that i have no complaint.
